OL,6,FA wife, on trial for the murder of her
OL,7,Fhusband and dumping his body at the
OL,8,Fbottom of the garden, has been found
OL,9,Fguilty.
OL,11,FCanterbury Crown Court heard that
OL,12,FMaureen Rickards had subjected her
OL,13,Fhusband to a campaign of abuse in the
OL,14,Fweeks leading up to his death.
OL,16,FJeremy Rickards, 65, had been reported
OL,17,Fmissing from the North Holmes Road
OL,18,Farea of Canterbury, Kent on 5 July
OL,19,F2024 having not been seen since 7 June.
