OL,6,FFollowing efforts to find him, his
OL,7,Fwife, Maureen Rickards, 50, was
OL,8,Farrested. Forensic teams attended the
OL,9,Faddress and three properties were
OL,10,Fcordoned off.
OL,12,FJeremy Rickards, was stabbed
OL,13,Frepeatedly in June 2024, with the
OL,14,Fpostmortem showing he had also been
OL,15,Fstrangled in the weeks before his
OL,16,Fdeath and that he was also recovering
OL,17,Ffrom recent rib fractures.
