OL,6,FWitnesses who saw him before his death
OL,7,Fand saw the extent of his injuries,
OL,8,Fincluding a large cut on his forehead
OL,9,Fand bruising to his eyes and ears,
OL,10,Fwere so concerned that they urged him
OL,11,Fto get hospital treatment.
OL,13,FIn the weeks following Jeremy's
OL,14,Fdisappearance, Rickards used his bank
OL,15,Fcards to go shopping in Canterbury,
OL,16,Fbefore messaging their daughter using
OL,17,Fthe victim's phone to say that her
OL,18,Ffather had arrived in Saudi Arabia.
