OL,6,FTheir daughter was concerned about the
OL,7,Fstyle of messages and asked if her
OL,8,Fmother had taken over her father's
OL,9,Fphone.
OL,11,FRickards messaged her daughter to say
OL,12,Fthat her father had taken his own life
OL,13,Fin Saudi Arabia, but later reported
OL,14,Fhim as missing to the police.
OL,16,FWhen officers checked the garden of
OL,17,Fthe property, they detected a smell in
OL,18,Fthe garden and found a bag with the
OL,19,Fremains of Jeremy's body.
