OL,6,FJames Fisher from the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service South East said:
OL,8,F"As we built the case against Maureen
OL,9,FRickards, we were able to unpick her
OL,10,Fweb of lies, using forensic evidence
OL,11,Fand her actions before and after the
OL,12,Fmurder, to paint the picture of a
OL,13,Fcallous abuser, who subjected Jeremy
OL,14,Fto unimaginable pain and suffering.
